17#ifndef RDATA_IN_1_DHCID_49_C
18#define RDATA_IN_1_DHCID_49_C 1

20#define RRTYPE_DHCID_ATTRIBUTES 0

22static inline isc_result_t
23fromtext_in_dhcid(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
24
25 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dhcid);
26 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
27
28 UNUSED(type);
29 UNUSED(rdclass);
30 UNUSED(origin);
31 UNUSED(options);
32 UNUSED(callbacks);
33
34 return (isc_base64_tobuffer(lexer, target, -2));
35}
36
37static inline isc_result_t
38totext_in_dhcid(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
39 isc_region_t sr, sr2;
40 /* " ; 64000 255 64000" */
41 char buf[5 + 3*11 + 1];
42
43 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dhcid);
44 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
45 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
46
47 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
48 sr2 = sr;
49
50 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
51 RETERR(str_totext("( " /*)*/, target));
52 if (tctx->width == 0) /* No splitting */
53 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sr, 60, "", target));
54 else
55 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sr, tctx->width - 2,
56 tctx->linebreak, target));
57 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0) {
58 RETERR(str_totext(/* ( */ " )", target));
59 if (rdata->length > 2) {
60 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), " ; %u %u %u",
61 sr2.base[0] * 256U + sr2.base[1],
62 sr2.base[2], rdata->length - 3U);
63 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
64 }
65 }
66 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
67}
68
69static inline isc_result_t
70fromwire_in_dhcid(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
71 isc_region_t sr;
72
73 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dhcid);
74 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
75
76 UNUSED(type);
77 UNUSED(rdclass);
78 UNUSED(dctx);
79 UNUSED(options);
80
81 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
82 if (sr.length == 0)
83 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
84
85 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr.length);
86 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
87}
88
89static inline isc_result_t
90towire_in_dhcid(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
91 isc_region_t sr;
92
93 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dhcid);
94 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
95 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
96
97 UNUSED(cctx);
98
99 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
100 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
101}
102
103static inline int
104compare_in_dhcid(ARGS_COMPARE) {
105 isc_region_t r1;
106 isc_region_t r2;
107
108 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
109 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
110 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_dhcid);
111 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
112 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
113 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
114
115 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
116 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
117 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
118}
119
120static inline isc_result_t
121fromstruct_in_dhcid(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
122 dns_rdata_in_dhcid_t *dhcid = source;
123
124 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dhcid);
125 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
126 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
127 REQUIRE(dhcid->common.rdtype == type);
128 REQUIRE(dhcid->common.rdclass == rdclass);
129 REQUIRE(dhcid->length != 0);
130
131 UNUSED(type);
132 UNUSED(rdclass);
133
134 return (mem_tobuffer(target, dhcid->dhcid, dhcid->length));
135}
136
137static inline isc_result_t
138tostruct_in_dhcid(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
139 dns_rdata_in_dhcid_t *dhcid = target;
140 isc_region_t region;
141
142 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dhcid);
143 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
144 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
145 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
146
147 dhcid->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
148 dhcid->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
149 ISC_LINK_INIT(&dhcid->common, link);
150
151 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
152
153 dhcid->dhcid = mem_maybedup(mctx, region.base, region.length);
154 if (dhcid->dhcid == NULL)
155 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
156
157 dhcid->mctx = mctx;
158 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
159}
160
161static inline void
162freestruct_in_dhcid(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
163 dns_rdata_in_dhcid_t *dhcid = source;
164
165 REQUIRE(dhcid != NULL);
166 REQUIRE(dhcid->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_dhcid);
167 REQUIRE(dhcid->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
168
169 if (dhcid->mctx == NULL)
170 return;
171
172 if (dhcid->dhcid != NULL)
173 isc_mem_free(dhcid->mctx, dhcid->dhcid);
174 dhcid->mctx = NULL;
175}

177static inline isc_result_t
178additionaldata_in_dhcid(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
179 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dhcid);
180 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
181
182 UNUSED(rdata);
183 UNUSED(add);
184 UNUSED(arg);
185
186 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
187}

189static inline isc_result_t
190digest_in_dhcid(ARGS_DIGEST) {
191 isc_region_t r;
192
193 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dhcid);
194 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
195
196 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
197
198 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
199}

202checkowner_in_dhcid(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
203
204 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dhcid);
205 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
206
207 UNUSED(name);
208 UNUSED(type);
209 UNUSED(rdclass);
210 UNUSED(wildcard);
211
212 return (true);
213}

220
221 UNUSED(rdata);
222 UNUSED(owner);

228static inline int
229casecompare_in_dhcid(ARGS_COMPARE) {
230 return (compare_in_dhcid(rdata1, rdata2));
231}
